层病案库病案架采购及安装项目 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目，具体货物名称、数量、规格及技术参数等以招标文件、技术要求、采购清单为准，招标人保留对上述招标范围进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">供货期要求：<span>15</span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bo