\r\n      <td width=\"33%\" style=\"width:33.88%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:\r\n      none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:2.85pt\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;line-height:23.0pt;\r\n      layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元以上</span></p>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td width=\"66%\" colspan=\"3\" style=\"width:66.1%;border-top:none;border-left:\r\n      none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n      padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:2.85pt\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:center;line-height:23.0pt;\r\n      layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">酌情考虑，不得大于<span>120</span>日历天</span></p>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<span>1</span>）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作业时限起始时间为</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中标人收到资料<span>2</span>日内检查资料完整性，如资料不全需列出具体清单报招标人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<span>2</span>）初审结果作业时限终止时间为：中标人提交待复审初审结果表之日。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<span>3</span>）审核意见及结果，书面报送招标人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上时间已包含除春节以外的所有节假日时间。若非招标人原因，没有按照规定时间完成，每逾期一天，招标人有权对中标人扣除<span>2000</span>元<span>/</span>天违约金，延误超过<span>10</span>天，招标人有权解除合同，同时乙方需承担由此对招标人造成的一切损失；若因审核时间延误对招标人造成重大影响的，招标人有权保留进一步对中标人索赔的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">、质量要求：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">初步成果文件应包含：编制说明、现场勘察记录、经复核的工程计算底稿、初步组价文件（纸质版、电子版）、核对过程中可能存在的争议点；中标人初步成果文件不得随意应付招标人，必须严格按照招标人要求计算，若经招标人发现，中标人未按招标人要求认真计算，招标人有权拒收中标人初步成果文件，同时对中标人扣除<span>5000</span>元<span>/</span>次违约金，工期不予顺延；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最终成果文件应包含：双方确认后的核定单、中标人内部三级复核、审定报告书、编制说明、核增核减明细、现场勘察记录、经核对的工程量计算底稿、组价文件、造价部门出具的争议答复（如有）；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.3 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中标人出具最终成果文件前应将全套资料报招标人复核，经招标人复核无误后方可出具报告盖章；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.4 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中标人需对出具的最终成果文件质量负责，最终成果文件经招标人复核：若单位工程出现<span>5</span>条清单及以上错误且单条清单经复核（单条清单总价复核前后对比）总价误差大于<span>10%</span>的，招标人有权对中标人处以<span>5000</span>元处罚；若单位工程出现<span>10</span>条清单及以上错误且单条清单经复核（单条清单总价复核前后对比）总价误差大于<span>20%</span>的，招标人有权扣除所有审计费，同时对招标人造成的一切损失均由中标人承担；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经审计局复审（如有），由一审单位提供审计局所需要的所有材料，并负责全过程对接。如一审审计金额和审计局复审金额有较大出入，导致招标人出现超付工程款等问题，超付金额由一审单位补缴给招标人，并负责向审计局解释原因，并承担相应责任，减少或消除对招标人带来的影响。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对于<span>1000</span>万元以上工程，在政府审计复审时，误差率≤<span>0.8%</span>，若因中标人原因导致误差率＞<span>0.8%</span>时，扣除该项目的全部服务费用；若因中标人原因导致误差率≥<span>1.0%</span>时，将被终止合同，同时按招标人相关规定对中标人进行处罚；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对于<span>1000</span>万元以下<span>100</span>万元以上工程，在政府审计复审时，误差率≤<span>1.0%</span>，若因中标人自身原因导致误差率＞<span>1.0%</span>时，扣除该项目的全部服务费用；若因中标人自身原因导致误差率≥<span>1.5%</span>时，将被终止合同，同时按招标人相关规定对中标人进行处罚；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对于<span>100</span>万元以下工程，在政府审计复审时，误差率≤<span>1.5%</span>，若因中标人自身原因导致误差率＞<span>1.5%</span>时，扣除该项目的全部服务费用；若因中标人自身原因导致误差率≥<span>2.0%</span>时，将被终止合同，同时按招标人相关规定对中标人进行处罚。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">招标人对中标人初步或最终成果复查发现问题，经中标人确认后仍以各种理由拒绝调整的，扣除<span>2000</span>元<span>/</span>次违约金；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.7 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中标人核对人员如不接受招标人考核、无故缺席或以各种理由拒绝核对的，每发现一次扣除<span>2000</span>元违约金。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.1pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">6</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、本次招标共确定三家服务单位，具体服务任务以招标人分配任务为准。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标人资格要求：投标人须是在中华人民共和国境内注册的具有完成本项目招标范围能力的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">、拟派人员的要求：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拟派人员具体包括（但不限于）以下人员（即按以下要求，至少应配备<span>6</span>名相关专业的造价人员）：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目负责人<span>1</span>名，必须是本单位在岗在职的一级注册造价工程师（旧版注册证书为造价工程师证书，不分等级），并具备建设工程类中级及以上职称；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除项目负责人外，项目组需配备土建、安装专业的一级注册造价工程师（旧版注册证书为造价工程师证书，不分等级）各<span>1</span>名，必须是本单位在岗在职的注册造价工程师；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.3 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目组其他造价人员不少于<span>3</span>名，必须是本单位在岗在职员工，具有二级及以上注册造价工程师。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上述人员均为本单位正式注册人员，最终人员数量根据项目实施需要进行调整，所有人员不得在两个或两个以上单位挂职。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">、本次招标一律不接受联合体和挂靠投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">、信誉要求：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.1</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">投标人近三年内没有严重违约和重大质量问题、安全事故、投标违规等不良记录而被政府有关部门处罚，没有处于被责令停业、财产被接管、冻结、破产等状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标人以不正当手段骗取中标，被建设行政主管部门或司法部门查处的，将被拒绝参与本工程投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">五、招标文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.85pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公告发布后，凡具备以上投标人资格要求，并自愿参加本次投标的投标人，须携带本单位介绍信或授权委托书以及购买人身份证原件于<b><span>2023</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>6</span>日至<span>2023</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>11</span>日止（上午<span>8:30-12</span>：<span>00</span>，下午<span>14:30-18:00</span>，节假日休息）</b>到盐城市招标代理有限公司（地址：盐城市钱江财富广场<span>A</span>座<span>3A</span>楼，联系人：张工，联系电话：<span>0515-89803566</span>、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">13921809379</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">）行政服务部报名并购买招标文件，投标人购买招标文件后方可参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>3000</span>元，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>综合评估法</b>，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">九、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：张工</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">0515-66698027</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：盐城市招标代理有限公司</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地址：盐城市青年路钱江财富广场西区</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">楼</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：吴女士</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电话：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">0515-89803566</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">15950298580</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('3066','3891','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目，资金已落实，现通过公开招标方式诚邀潜在的投标人参加本项目的投标工作。1、工程概况 1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目 1.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1683275448','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目，资金已落实，现通过公开招标方式诚邀潜在的投标人参加本项目的投标工作。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程概况<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区负二层病案库病案架采购及安装项目，具体货物名称、数量、规格及技术参数等以招标文件、技术要求、采购清单为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">供货期要求：<span>15</span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">最高限价：<span>17.55 </span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人必须是在中国境内注册，有独立完成本项目所有工作的能力的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2023</span>年<span>2</span>月的某一天，则投标人需保证以上人员<span>2022</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>-2023</span>年<span>1</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）（投标时提供社保证明材料）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">楼</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">805</span><span style=\"background:white\">室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2023</span><span style=\"background:\r\nwhite\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">6</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">时</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">30</span><span style=\"background:white\">分至</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2023</span><span style=\"background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">\r\n<span>5</span></span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">11</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">18</span><span style=\"background:white\">时。联系人：刘工，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-69057406</span><span style=\"background:white\">；手机：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">13626222271</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">、</span><b>评标办法</b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">:</span></b><b>采用“经评审的最低投标价法”。</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"background:white\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-66696810</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地址：盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：张女士</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系电话：<span>0515-66696855 </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地址：盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>805</span>室</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：刘工</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电话：<span>0515-69057406</span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('3067','3892','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院2023年纸类用品采购项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、盐城市招标代理有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。二、符合本项目招标','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1683275503','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;background:white\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">盐城市第一人民医院<span>2023</span>年纸类用品采购项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">一、盐城市招标代理有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">二、符合本项目招标公告资格要求的投标的申请人均可参加该项目投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目名称</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院<span>2023</span>年纸类用品采购项目</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供货地点</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院，具体供货地点根据招标人要求。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">、招标规模：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目采购预算约<span>48.9</span>万元</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">、招标范围及内容：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院<span>2023</span>年纸类用品采购及供应，具体供货内容及数量详见项目清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">服务期及</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供货时间要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">5.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供货期：一年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">5.2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供货时间要求：供货时间根据招标人需求在规定时间内供应并确保使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、质量标准：符合招标文件中技术需求、国家现行的相关规范标准及有关部门最新颁布的相应的最新标准。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、质量要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">7.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量要求：国家“合格”标准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">7.2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质保期：易耗品质保期以产品标明的保质期时间为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;background:white\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、投标人须是在中国境内注册且有能力独立完成本次招标内容的独立法人或自然人或其他组织。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;background:white\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、投标人必须具有独立承担民事责任和履行合同能力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">所投产品的生产厂家具有</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有效期内的<span>ISO9001</span>质量管理体系认证证书</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、<span>CFCC/PEFC</span>认证的中国森林认证证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;background:white\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、投标人近三年内没有严重违约和重大质量问题、安全事故、投标违规等不良记录而被政府有关部门处罚，没有处于被责令停业、财产被接管、冻结、破产等状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;background:white\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、本次招标人一律不接受联合体投标，中标后不得以任何方式进行转包与分包。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、投标人应遵守国家和省、市的有关法律、法规和政策，且没有违法违规的行为。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">五、招标文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.85pt;line-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公告发布后，凡具备以上投标人资格要求，并自愿参加本次投标的投标人，须携带本单位介绍信或授权委托书以及购买人身份证原件于<b><span>2023</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>6</span>日至<span>2023</span>年<span>5</span>月<span>11</span>日止（上午<span>8:30-12</span>：<span>00</span>，下午<span>14:30-18:00</span>，节假日休息）</b>到盐城市招标代理有限公司（地址：盐城市钱江财富广场<span>A</span>座<span>3A</span>楼，联系人：张工，联系电话：<span>0515-89803566</span>、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#444444\">13921809379</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）行政服务部报名并购买招标文件，投标人购买招标文件后方可参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.1pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#444444\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#444444\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>8000</span>元，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#444444\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>综合评估法</b>，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#444444\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text