ze:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">服务地点：盐城市第一人民医院北院区。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院北区电梯无线对讲采购及安装项目，具体详见项目需求。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">符合国家及行业规范“合格”标准</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">工期：<span>15</span>个日历天。具体开始日期以招标人的通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">最高限价：<span>4.3</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应具有独立法人资格，能够独立承担民事责任的能力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2023</span>年<span>2</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2022</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>-2023</span>年<span>1</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）（投标时提供社保证明材料）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bo