></p><p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p><p style=\"background: white; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 21pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none;\"><span style=\"background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast;\">6</span><span style=\"background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast;\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话</span></p><p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p><p style=\"background: white; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 21pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none;\"><span style=\"background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast;\">盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p><p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p><p style=\"background: white; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast;\">7</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast;\">、联系方式</span></b></p><p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p><p style=\"background: white; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 21pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: 